OL,7,FDisruption across the Tyne and Wear
OL,8,FMetro network is continuing as the
OL,9,Ffleet undergoes checks for faults
OL,10,Fwhich "will take several days".
OL,12,FNexus advised commuters against
OL,13,Ftravelling at rush hour on Monday 22
OL,14,FJuly due to a reduced service causing
OL,15,Fgaps between trains of up to 24 mins.
OL,17,FIn a statement from the operator,
OL,18,FNexus said: "Metro is operating to all
OL,19,Fstations but there are gaps between
OL,20,Ftrains of up to 24 minutes on the
OL,21,FGreen Line and on the Yellow Line.
