OL,7,F"We advise our customers to avoid
OL,8,Ftravel during the rush hour if they
OL,9,Fcan or to seek alternative transport,
OL,10,Fleave extra time for journeys if you
OL,11,Fare travelling by Metro.
OL,13,F"Our train supplier, Stadler, has
OL,14,Ffound a fault in part of the
OL,15,Fpantograph that draws power from the
OL,16,Foverhead line.
