OL,7,FIt is understood that the carbon
OL,8,Fstrips on all trains are being checked
OL,9,Fto make sure they are not faulty.
OL,11,FThe service is operating to all
OL,12,Fdestinations but eight trains are
OL,13,Fcurrently out of action.
OL,15,FITV News Tyne Tees has approached
OL,16,FStadler for comment.
